Nothing scary about a beautiful new bathroom.
#repost • @edbyellen Enter to WIN a $5,000 Bathroom Makeover! Is your current bathroom a nightmare? If so, Ellen wants to see it for a chance to win the bathroom of your dreams - including ED Ellen DeGeneres vanities, storage, lighting and bath linens. 

Enter the ED Ellen DeGeneres Bathroom Makeover Sweepstakes between now and 8/31/21: Follow @EDbyEllen on Instagram, snap and share a picture of your nightmare bathroom and post to your instagram feed, tag @EDbyEllen and use the hash tag #EDbathSweepstakes to be entered. You can enter up to 10 times a week (50 times max). 

The $5,000 prize includes: $3000 in credit towards any vanity, mirror or storage cabinet on https://bath.edbyellen.com/, $1000 in credit on lighting or bath linens on https://www.edbyellen.com, and a $1000 VISA gift card!

Winner will be randomly selected on 9/2 and notified via Instagram direct message from @EDbyEllen. No Purch. Nec. Ends 8/31/21. 18+, US only, Rules: https://EDbathSweepstakes.prizelogic.com

node.text: #regram • @theellenfund Chimpanzees are so special. Whether they are touching their toes or our hearts we must make sure they are safe. On World Chimpanzee Day we are calling attention to an urgent situation in California. These chimps need help now to find new homes. ellen.tv/3hCX6Ab #WorldChimpanzeeDay #chimpanzee #chimp #rescue @napsaprimates #chimpsinneed
